entry.def: An annexe is a building which is joined to or is next to a larger main building.

example.ex: ...setting up a museum in an annexe to the theatre.

entry.def: An annexe to a document is a section added to it at the end.

example.ex: The Annex lists and discusses eight titles.
example.tran: 附录列举并讨论了8本书。
